    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/678de1b3c8a56740f1a9160b2f339a19.avif?t=1757702469\" width=615 height=90 /></span><br>数百年前，一颗陨石降落至地球表面，带来毁灭性冲击，引发一系列灾难，整个世界千疮百孔，人类文明近乎灭绝。<br><br>从那天起，一种名为幻灵的新生命开始出现在世界各地。你被选为召唤师，成为精英组织的一员，控制幻灵来维护人类仅存的堡垒——阿卡迪亚城的秩序。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/57a9d21b25cc6b39dc6d5f99113f408a.poster.avif?t=1757702469\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/57a9d21b25cc6b39dc6d5f99113f408a.webm?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/57a9d21b25cc6b39dc6d5f99113f408a.mp4?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/5a9bc0c41525fd39284bdb019cb2c35b.avif?t=1757702469\" width=615 height=90 /></span><br>收集上百种幻灵纳入你的队伍，每种幻灵皆有其独特的元素属性及特征。通过幻灵结合，大大提升队伍能力，让你的幻灵继承其他幻灵的独特特征。结合效果充满无限可能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/5bca8f1e391db96c924fe05017931c81.poster.avif?t=1757702469\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/5bca8f1e391db96c924fe05017931c81.webm?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/5bca8f1e391db96c924fe05017931c81.mp4?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/6a7cde605c8c3cb955d32f15d81fc881.avif?t=1757702469\" width=615 height=90 /></span><br>遇见各种各样激动人心、别具一格的角色，并与之并肩作战。帮助他们克服身心上的种种困难，在重重挑战与艰险逆境面前缔结坚不可摧的纽带。这些纽带将坚定你成为召唤师的决心，并将其化为陪你作战到底的强大伙伴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/264a7aae00b5fad13aee7a82e450a8ad.poster.avif?t=1757702469\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/264a7aae00b5fad13aee7a82e450a8ad.webm?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/264a7aae00b5fad13aee7a82e450a8ad.mp4?t=1757702469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273720/extras/97fde959777db7f0aacfb24d60556741.avif?t=1757702469\" width=615 height=90 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>收集召唤大量各具特色的幻灵。<br></li><li>挑战富有难度的回合制战斗，获得战略性队伍建设和巧妙决策能力。<br></li><li>无需不必要的刷怪，即可体验旨在提升玩家个性表达的丰富自定义配队。<br></li><li>集结最强盟友，与之并肩作战，提升你作为召唤师的技能。<br></li><li>体验一个设定于数百年后扣人心弦的后末日故事。</li></ul>",
